data.description: This 1,740 sq. ft. classic home can be customized to your liking.  Prime location with gorgeous view of the San Jacinto mountains, near the Palms Village Park and the famous El Paseo shops and restaurants.  Situated on a huge .26 acre lot with 3 bedrooms, a bonus room, 2 upgraded full bathrooms, open living/dining room floor plan, vaulted ceiling, and newer HVAC system.  Kitchen includes a breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances, including a Viking gas stove, refrigerator and new dishwasher, with direct access to an attached 2 car garage.  Outdoor space includes  a gated front patio and a large backyard with RV parking, dog kennel, built in shed with electricity, variety of fruit trees, and a running water fountain.  Shown by appointment only.  Text LA to schedule.
